full_title: The Craving (Jenna’s Version) by twenty one pilots
title: The Craving (Jenna’s Version)

description.plain:
“The Craving (Jenna’s Version)” is the fourth song by twenty one pilots that is dedicated to/inspired by Tyler Joseph’s wife, Jenna Joseph, following “Tear in My Heart,” “Smithereens,” and “Formidable.”

The song sees Tyler contemplating if he’s providing enough love in his relationship to his partner Jenna, over ukulele production.

twenty one pilots previewed the song for the very first time at their show at the Electric Ballroom in London on May 9th, 2024. The single version was released on May 22nd, and the version of the song on Clancy was released on May 24th, 2024, alongside the album.
